<h2>Your Account Has Been Suspended</h2>

<p>Hello [% user.first_name || user.username || 'there' %],</p>

<p>Your [% sitename || 'Comserv' %] account has been suspended.</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Account:</strong> [% user.username %] ([% user.email %])</li>
    [% IF suspended_at %]<li><strong>Suspended at:</strong> [% suspended_at %]</li>[% END %]
    [% IF reason %]<li><strong>Reason:</strong> [% reason %]</li>[% END %]
</ul>

<p>While your account is suspended, you will not be able to log in to [% sitename || 'Comserv' %].</p>

<p>If you believe this suspension was made in error or you would like to appeal, please contact the site administrator.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The [% sitename || 'Comserv' %] Team</p>
